{"tid":757924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(你個野壞左阿.jpg) 湖北食藥監局：40萬支不合格疫苗因設備故障導致所致 恢復生產","createTime":"2018-07-27T08:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T18:06:12.000Z","uid":58958,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd03ab49f746888ca74396584a4f17be2a372381","tid":757924,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"人民網北京7月27日電 （朱江）據湖北省食品藥品監督管理局網站消息，湖北省食品藥品監督管理局昨日發布公告稱，對武漢生物制品研究所有限公司效價不合格疫苗的原因及流向、處置等問題作出回答。<br />\n<br />\n問：武漢生物制品研究所有限公司（以下簡稱武生所）生產的201607050-2批次疫苗效價不合格的原因是什麽？<br />\n<br />\n答：經現場檢查發現，造成涉事批次疫苗效價低於國家標準規定的主要原因是：分裝設備短時間故障導致待分裝產品混懸液的不均勻所致。<br />\n<br />\n問：武生所生產的201607050-2批次效價不合格疫苗流向了哪裏？如何處置的？<br />\n<br />\n答：武生所2016年生產的201607050-2批次效價不合格疫苗共計400520支，分別銷往重慶市和河北省疾病預防控制中心。未使用的疫苗全部封存並由涉事企業召回，於2018年5月4日在武漢市食品藥品監管局的監督下進行了銷毀。2018年2月，原國家衛生計生委和原國家食品藥品監管總局已部署安排河北省、重慶市接種過上述不合格批次百白破疫苗的兒童開展補種工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/164206_5a16bd1100f32105a1a135391616f03c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F164206_5a16bd1100f32105a1a135391616f03c.png&h=6fa76044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKeep 住打啦喂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed24668905f6291c8d14ce03dff889cb9eac62fc","tid":757924,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800edf895d5fae31d06f4d8cfafe4b249e5c7914","tid":757924,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"022639d6ef7d75e73025835da1e26341406628e1","tid":757924,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"環球時報總編請先打，之後到刁種，克強，再之後到老董、689。<br />\n<br />\n即時生產，隨機抽一支打"},{"pid":"5bef06e7ffff8aaa2ee2cfc97f4dd71974611284","tid":757924,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"支持繼續打"},{"pid":"66de223d11004a1da93cd91de7fc5bcc0bff7893","tid":757924,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"死多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45c1183d041b6e6046cf72c153d64c43a358105","tid":757924,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcd8ec5a934062867bedf3a15d098ba1d019214a","tid":757924,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"我信呀！快啲同國內同胞講唔洗蒞香港呢啲二線城市打針"},{"pid":"c8224edfdc201079559f906d3becd26027bd1d9f","tid":757924,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"即係拆掂左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知洗左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4650d91e7bc436183eaa43d3d9cc7fbc0ce76c40","tid":757924,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"同胞放心打啦"},{"pid":"43cd32e771c9e1269867e123f49c2c81492fb3e0","tid":757924,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"根本上就冇問題，反而香港的疫苗質素仲差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1572b476dce71b2cfac6a094c1306f1e06d219","tid":757924,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffadabe7adf8b1b7abd538ad04e780180af31c9e","tid":757924,"uid":142067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a799df02031a4038d5a64f1c6591f1b9424983","tid":757924,"uid":53811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim